dct_title_s: A new map of Spain and Portugal divided into their respective kingdoms and provinces from the latest authorities
dct_description_sm: Scales include "Spanish and Portuguese leagues", "common French leagues" and "British statute miles." Pictorial relief. From: Cary's new universal atlas ... London : Printed for J. Cary ... , 1808.
